summaries.short: After Jimmy and Pussy are arrested in an FBI raid, Makazian tells Tony that Pussy may be wired for the Feds.
summaries.full: After Jimmy and Pussy are arrested in an FBI raid, Makazian tells a stunned Tony that Pussy may be wired for the Feds. Tony sends Paulie to find out for sure. Later, Tony learns that Makazian might be trying to frame Pussy to get out of his gambling debts.

summaries.short: Christopher and Adrianna cut a deal with a famous gangsta rapper. Tony plays golf with Cusamano and his friends.
summaries.full: Christopher and Adrianna cut a deal with a famous gangsta rapper who claims that Hesh pocketed royalties belonging to a cousin who recorded several hit songs decades ago. Meanwhile, Tony plays golf with Cusamano and his white-bread friends.

summaries.short: Season Two opens with Tony adjusting to life in the aftermath of a federal crackdown.
summaries.full: Season Two opens with the aftermath of the federal crackdown: Junior's in jail, Melfi refuses to see Tony, Christopher's expanding into new business ventures, Pussy is still missing...and Tony's adjusting to life as the new boss. To complicate matters even more, Tony's free-spirited sister Janice arrives to take care of Livia.

Upset that he isn't getting the notoriety of other family members, an agitated Christopher has an ugly encounter with a bakery clerk.
